  "body": "A few things seem to differ, unnecessarily (IMO). \r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/execution-apis/blob/main/src/engine/specification.md#executionpayloadv1\r\n\r\n`receiptRoot` very close but eth1 calls it `receiptsRoot`\r\n`blockNumber` eth1 calls it simply `number`\r\n\r\nIf these discrepancies are intentional and motivated, feel free to ignore this ticket and just close it. I'm just bringing it up in case it's just oversights that can/should be aligned. ",
